    "en": "For patients with Mild Cognitive Impairment (MCI), a careful sleep history, including assessment of sleep time, insomnia, daytime sleepiness, napping, and REM sleep behaviour disorder may facilitate identification of pre-clinical dementia, or high risk of developing dementia, and should be included in the assessments.",
